es biometrics and zero-knowledge proofs to verify humanity in the face of n=
ew challenges presented by AI.=C2=A0
Astro Mechanica [ https://substack.com/redirect/06a440fc-4b3f-4df9-bdd8-10f=
fb560e8b9?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNp=
U ] plans to make supersonic flight economical thanks to advances in electr=
ic motors and direct-to-consumer booking.=C2=A0
Helion [ https://substack.com/redirect/02fa6f09-c4d9-4ec9-b7de-f39dee4531ea=
?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] CEO D=
avid Kirtley credits advancements in pulsed power electronics, fiber optic =
cables, simulation software, FPGAs, mechanical structural codes, and power =
electronics codes with making fusion possible today. =E2=80=9CIt=E2=80=99s =
less on the physics,=E2=80=9D he said, =E2=80=9Cand more on =E2=80=98How ar=
e you building a company?=E2=80=99=E2=80=9D=C2=A0
They=E2=80=99re not defined by the technology they use, but by how they bui=
ld companies using technology to solve challenges. And, if they=E2=80=99re =
successful, they come to define sectors previously unscathed by modern tech=
nology.=C2=A0
