1?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] is t=
he prime example. It=E2=80=99s considered a =E2=80=9Cdeep tech=E2=80=9D com=
pany, but really, it=E2=80=99s a Techno-Industrial. And it highlights the i=
mportance of analyzing when the tools are good enough for a Techno-Industri=
