Anduril and Power Laws
When Anduril launched in 2017, it was famously met with a ton of skepticism=
=2E Some of it came from the fact that=20=
investors found defense distasteful, b=
ut a lot of it came from a lack of knowledge about the defense industry.=C2=
=A0
