=2E America=E2=80=99s industrial base has=20=
atrophied. The biggest systems in t=
he world need to be rebuilt.=C2=A0
Enormous Markets. Most of the largest companies by revenue are not tech com=
panies, and most of the world=E2=80=99s GDP is outside of tech: in energy, =
healthcare, labor, real estate, and manufacturing. These are multi-trillion=
