Examples. Companies like Anduril, Tesla, and SpaceX have shown founders tha=
t it=E2=80=99s possible to build enormous businesses by building hard thing=
s.=C2=A0
I=E2=80=99ve spent the last few months studying Techno-Industrials by divin=
g deep on specific companies, and I=E2=80=99m starting to see some patterns=
=2E Obviously, these companies aren=E2=
=80=99t successful yet, but there lesso=
ns in the way they=E2=80=99re thinking about their opportunities.=C2=A0
Take Base Power Company [ https://substack.com/redirect/70aca328-8887-441d-=
b820-e0b98edcf701?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6=
