Investing in Techno-Industrials
One of the most common pieces of skepticism I faced raising Not Boring Capi=
tal Fund III was that LPs didn=E2=80=99t like that I invest in crypto and d=
eep tech.=C2=A0
That=E2=80=99s on me. I didn=E2=80=99t do a good job explaining what I actu=
ally invest in =E2=80=93 companies using whatever technologies necessary to=
